vote.title: Authorize an amendment to the service contract with Oak Cliff Empowered, Inc., previously approved by Resolution No. 19-0433, on March 27, 2019 to increase it by $93,623.00, from $374,493.00 to $468,116.00 to: (1) provide additional funding for a 7th cohort of workforce training participants; and (2) extend the term of the contract through October 31, 2022 - Not to exceed $93,623.00 - Financing: Public/Private Partnership Fund
